PN,31101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FThe UK will still support "the people
OL,7,Fand places that need it most" the
OL,8,Fforeign secretary has insisted,
OL,9,Fdespite widespread cuts to the
OL,10,Finternational aid budget.
OL,12,FYvette Cooper has admitted that cuts
OL,13,Fto the aid budget mean there will be
OL,14,F"hard choices and unavoidable trade-
OL,15,Foffs" - but insisted that the UK will
OL,16,Fremain a "major player" in overseas
OL,17,Faid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FThe widespread cuts to the aid budget
OL,7,Fannounced last year will see aid
OL,8,Fspending fall from 0.5% of GDP to 0.3%
OL,9,Fby 2028-29 - as Cooper announced cuts
OL,10,Fto grants across the world, including
OL,11,Fconflict-struck nations like Yemen and
OL,12,FAfghanistan.
OL,14,FLabour MPs have criticised the
OL,15,Fdecision, with some warning it could
OL,16,Fweaken the UK's defence and drive
OL,17,Fglobal migration in an increasingly
OL,18,Ffragile world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FCooper's statement on Thursday came
OL,7,Fafter the conflict in the Middle East
OL,8,Fintensified following Iran's latest
OL,9,Fround of strikes.
OL,11,FThe cuts to international aid were
OL,12,Fannounced in February last year, as
OL,13,Fthe Chancellor told MPs that the money
OL,14,Fwas needed to pay for an increase in
OL,15,Fdefence spending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FAt the time, the decision was met with
OL,7,Fbacklash from senior Labour MPs and
OL,8,Forganisations working in the sector
OL,9,Fwho called the move "short-sighted"
OL,10,Fand a "betrayal of the world's most
OL,11,Fvulnerable children".
OL,13,FOn Thursday, Cooper confirmed that the
OL,14,Fcuts will go ahead - and explained
OL,15,Fthat the government will now
OL,16,F"prioritise" countries wracked by war,
OL,17,Flike Ukraine, Gaza and Sudan.
OL,19,FPakistan and Mozambique are set to be
OL,20,Fthe worst hit - with significant
OL,21,Freductions to their funding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FCountries like Yemen, Somalia and
OL,7,FAfghanistan will also see reductions
OL,8,Fto grants they receive - though the
OL,9,FForeign office insist they will remain
OL,10,F"humanitarian priorities".
OL,12,FCooper also confirmed on Thursday that
OL,13,Fthe government will no longer pay G20
OL,14,Fcountries - apart from Turkey - to
OL,15,Fsupport refugees as the UK under a
OL,16,Fscheme of "bilateral aid payments".
OL,18,F"Allocating a reduced budget
OL,19,Finevitably leads to hard choices and
OL,20,Funavoidable trade-offs," Cooper told
OL,21,FMPs
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,F"So we're focusing aid on the people
OL,7,Fand places that need it most, and we
OL,8,Fwill still be a major player, and
OL,9,Fexpect to be the fifth biggest funder
OL,10,Fin the world."
OL,12,FShe added that fighting gendered
OL,13,Fviolence remained a top priority for
OL,14,Fthe government - amidst criticism from
OL,15,FLabour MPs and international aid
OL,16,Fcharities that women and girls will
OL,17,F"bear the brunt" of the cuts.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
