CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FITV News accompanied the foreign
OL,7,Fsecretary on a visit to Chad earlier
OL,8,Fthis year, where she met Sudanese
OL,9,Fwomen and girls living in the world's
OL,10,Flargest refugee camp.
OL,12,F"I have taken the decision to make
OL,13,Fsupport for women and girls not just
OL,14,Fthe priority for development, but a
OL,15,Fcentral theme across the work of the
OL,16,FForeign, Commonwealth and Development
OL,17,FOffice," Cooper insisted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
