PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,F"That means work to prevent violence,
OL,7,Fto champion political and economic
OL,8,Fparticipation and to keep children
OL,9,Flearning even during conflict."
OL,11,FBut several Labour MPs - including the
OL,12,FChair of the International Development
OL,13,Fcommittee Sarah Champion - have hit
OL,14,Fout at the decision to slash the aid
OL,15,Fbudget.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
