FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FChampion - who is also the MP for
OL,7,FRotherham - said she worried cuts to
OL,8,Faid in favour of defence budgets would
OL,9,Ftake away the "first line of defence"
OL,10,Fwhen it comes to preventing global
OL,11,Fconflicts.
OL,13,F"We have had defence pitched against
OL,14,Finternational development," she said,
OL,15,Freferencing what she sees as the
OL,16,Fgovernment's justification of the cuts.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,F"If you ask any military person, they
OL,7,Fwill tell you the best line of
OL,8,Fprevention and first defence is our
OL,9,Fdevelopment money because it keeps
OL,10,Fpeople safe and secure in their homes.
OL,11,FIt keeps them prosperous, it holds
OL,12,Fgovernments to account."
OL,14,F"I am very fearful in the world that
OL,15,Fwe find ourselves in, that taking that
OL,16,Ffirst line of defence away is going to
OL,17,Fhave massive consequences."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
