OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FShe added that she thinks the cuts
OL,12,Fcould lead to rising immigration, with
OL,13,Fmore people from war-torn countries
OL,14,Farriving on the UK's "shores".
OL,16,FCooper said in response that the
OL,17,Fgovernment acknowledged the link
OL,18,Fbetween aid and global security and
OL,19,Finsisted she was prioritising some
OL,20,F"conflict-affected" countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
