PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FThe Labour MP for York Rachael Maskell
OL,7,Falso called on the government to
OL,8,Fincrease aid spending.
OL,10,F"Without, we know that more children
OL,11,Fwill miss out on their education and
OL,12,Fvaccinations, women will have poorer
OL,13,Fhealth and people will experience
OL,14,Fgreater hunger and disease," she said
OL,15,Fin a parliamentary debate on the topic
OL,16,Fon Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
