FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FLeading charities have also raised the
OL,7,Falarm about what reducing aid to
OL,8,Fcertain countries could mean - hitting
OL,9,Fout at Keir Starmer for allowing what
OL,10,Fthey see as a "retreat from the UK's
OL,11,Fleadership role" on the world's stage.
OL,13,FAdrian Lovett, UK executive director
OL,14,Fof the One Campaign said deep cuts
OL,15,Fwould see hospitals and schools close
OL,16,Fin some of the world's poorest
OL,17,Fcountries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,F"At a moment of growing global
OL,7,Finstability, this is a retreat from
OL,8,Fthe UK's leadership role that will
OL,9,Fmake us less secure here at home and
OL,10,Fdevastate the lives of some of the
OL,11,Fworld's most vulnerable people," he
OL,12,Fadded.
OL,14,FActionAid - a leading charity which
OL,15,Fworks across 44 countries to support
OL,16,Fwomen and girls living in poverty -
OL,17,Falso raised the alarm about how the
OL,18,Ffunding cuts could harm the fight
OL,19,Fagainst the "economic and political
OL,20,Fsystems that violate the rights of
OL,21,Fwomen".
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
