PN,31115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774012288
OL,3,CGovernment confirms aid budget cuts
OL,4,Cdespite warnings from MPs
OL,6,FIn a statement shared with ITV News,
OL,7,Fthey said the Foreign Secretary's
OL,8,Fwords on the importance of fighting
OL,9,Fgendered violence felt "hollow".
OL,11,F"We're pleased to see the Foreign
OL,12,FSecretary acknowledge that women and
OL,13,Fgirls disproportionately bear the
OL,14,Fbrunt of poverty, violence and
OL,15,Fconflict by promising to make them a
OL,16,Fpriority ` but without backing up this
OL,17,Fpledge with increased long-term
OL,18,Ffunding, it rings hollow," they said.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
